{"id": 1108, "genre": 1001, "title": "影视剧里的职场和现实有哪些差别？", "description": "现实里应该不会出现“哟，是什么风把您吹来了！”这种话吧？（题图来自：Marion Fayolle）", "record_count": 4205, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160710220023901WzdQ2jJugq6V8.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-20T03:00:55Z", "options": [{"id": 102145, "content": "我还是很受伤就是借尸还魂嫁鸡随鸡 嫁狗随狗，接受事实。笨笨大好河山宝宝身上包包时尚女包很受伤嫁鸡随鸡世界顶级设计还是觉得好今生今世绘声绘色接受事实的宝贝很深很深很受伤很受伤很深很深还是睡吧睡吧半身不遂还是睡吧睡吧睡吧女学霸赫本恤衫男的不喝酒不抽烟不酗酒者可联系本人。半身不遂宝贝们", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692277}, {"id": 100098, "content": "你的总裁绝不是霸道帅气的小鲜肉老干部而是拿着爷爷叔叔或爷叔", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685868}, {"id": 102147, "content": "给哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692277}, {"id": 100100, "content": "好像没有霸道总裁…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646232}, {"id": 100104, "content": "现实真有………", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609852}, {"id": 100105, "content": "律师没有电视剧那么好当", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664161}, {"id": 100106, "content": "坚持原则不会得到提拔重用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685925}, {"id": 100107, "content": "醒工砖", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 100108, "content": "只有学历和能力一致才能入职。但社会上最看重学历和面貌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685949}, {"id": 100110, "content": "但社会上更看重学历和面貌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685949}, {"id": 100111, "content": "没那么多浪漫的桥段，拒绝傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683282}, {"id": 100116, "content": "并没有那么多勾心斗角", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682748}, {"id": 100117, "content": "你所有的不安全感都在被老板关注的时候被无限放大", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642858}, {"id": 100118, "content": "除了颜，除了钱，你还剩下什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642858}, {"id": 100119, "content": "走过最深的路还是套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642858}, {"id": 100120, "content": "多么痛的领悟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570869}, {"id": 100121, "content": "电视剧里穷到死天天被追债的人也能租的起月租上万的房子 用各种奢侈品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686004}, {"id": 100122, "content": "现实很残酷 没有人性", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492630}, {"id": 100125, "content": "剧里的都太明显.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686016}, {"id": 100126, "content": "下班后一脸的油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656113}, {"id": 100382, "content": "并没那么多像安迪的人 来帮你，更没有曲潇潇来和你交朋友（ps：并没那么绝对啊）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687107}, {"id": 100127, "content": "呵呵", "image": "img/option/option/20160721000535dgShWjq0Z7auvOxU", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685517}, {"id": 102178, "content": "如果有人说你傻逼，不是因为她们嫉妒你的美貌和善良，嫉妒你被总裁和客户同时看上，嫉妒你充满了才干还单纯不做作，多半因为你真的很傻逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693633}, {"id": 100131, "content": "真正的没有人做牛做马踢所有人掏腰包买外卖吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686090}, {"id": 100132, "content": "平均颜值并没有电视剧那么高………某些大咖并不是西装革履而是拖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674638}, {"id": 100135, "content": "职场都是上班工作，下班散伙，一般不会再黏在一起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680539}, {"id": 106791, "content": "老板出错，不是为了考验，如果你这样想，“开除！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 100138, "content": "医生没那么高薪也没有那么轻松", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676338}, {"id": 100140, "content": "不过真的像电视剧一样步步惊心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683792}, {"id": 101166, "content": "千钧一发之际的神奇逆转", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688960}, {"id": 100147, "content": "剧里总是过于夸张", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686199}, {"id": 105523, "content": "上司不会辣么帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672607}, {"id": 100404, "content": "現實中沒人想知道那電影中熱血的過程…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374921}, {"id": 100151, "content": "不会每天感觉除了勾心斗角什么都没做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686205}, {"id": 100152, "content": "出差并不是去纽约巴黎伦敦或者北上广，而是三四线城市的无名小厂。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562205}, {"id": 100153, "content": "关键看你入了哪行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686209}, {"id": 100154, "content": "我明明应该是主角，却没有光环。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686244}, {"id": 100158, "content": "总裁永远是总裁 没有故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412144}, {"id": 100166, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686254}, {"id": 100167, "content": "傻白甜早被劝退了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686254}, {"id": 100169, "content": "加班时并不会被老板默默的看到\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686304}, {"id": 100173, "content": "没有那么多gay，\r\n有的是真的，\r\n有的是装的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572045}, {"id": 100175, "content": "两个世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686018}, {"id": 100188, "content": "没有霸道总裁~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686358}, {"id": 110433, "content": "哪有那么多人上班全套妆化得整整齐齐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725051}, {"id": 109154, "content": "没有美女帅哥，没有帅气的霸道总裁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 723878}, {"id": 104039, "content": "剧里早上起床后有很多时间化妆 试衣服 卷头发 现实生活中并没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700770}, {"id": 171889, "content": "勇于跟领导对着干并得到提升是做梦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949444}, {"id": 112498, "content": "办公室恋情哪有那么频繁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743052}, {"id": 100479, "content": "看职场剧的往往不是职场人，但可能是职场人的妈妈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687558}]}